The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Metro shield

 New Delhi, April 3: Delhi Metro will soon have a dedicated security wing to fend off possible terrorist strikes, reports our special correspondent

 Manned by 2,900 personnel, the wing ? covering the 65-km Metro stretch ? will be modelled on the lines of the National Security Guards and the Special Protection Group. 




